msgid "0:[name]？？？[line]「――私は、もう天成神光会に戻る気はない」[%p]"
msgstr "0:[name]？？？[line]I'm not going back to the Cosmic Church of the Divine Light.[%p]"

msgid "100:[name]？？？[line]「実に惜しいね。君の才能を、私は買っていたのだが」[%p]"
msgstr "100:[name]？？？[line]A shame, really. I had such a high opinion of your talents.[%p]"

msgid "200:[name]？？？[line]「利用していた、の間違いだろう。私はもうあなたの言葉は信じない。教祖としての倉持雄大など虚像でしかないと分かった」[%p]"
msgstr "200:[name]？？？[line]You mean you were using me. I don't believe anything you say anymore. I know that the public image of Yudai Kuramochi, the great holy church leader, is nothing but a lie.[%p]"

msgid "300:[name]？？？[line]「神光の救いを、君も欲していただろう？」[%p]"
msgstr "300:[name]？？？[line]You wanted the Salvation of the Divine Light, didn't you?[%p]"

msgid "400:[name]？？？[line]「かつての私は、欲していた。だが、今は違う」[%p]"
msgstr "400:[name]？？？[line]I did, once, but not anymore.[%p]"

msgid "500:[name]？？？[line]「では、なにを欲しているのかね？」[%p]"
msgstr "500:[name]？？？[line]So, what do you want now, then?[%p]"

msgid "600:[name]？？？[line]「……償いのための、死だ」[%p]"
msgstr "600:[name]？？？[line]Death. Atonement.[%p]"

msgid "700:[name]？？？[line]「一度、神光に触れた者は、離れることなどできないよ。君は離れたつもりでも、神光はいかなる者をも見捨てない」[%p]"
msgstr "700:[name]？？？[line]Those who have touched the Divine Light once can no longer leave its grace. You may think you've left it behind, but the light will never leave you.[%p]"

msgid "800:[name]？？？[line]「神に頼る気は、もうない。神に匹敵する物を創ってしまった私には、神にすがることは許されない」[%p]"
msgstr "800:[name]？？？[line]I'm done relying on God for help. I've created something whose power rivals God. He will not allow me to receive his salvation.[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]セナ[line]「西條。起きろ、西條……！」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]セナ[line]Nishijo! Wake up, Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "1000:聞き慣れない男たちの、やけに仰々しいやり取り。その合間に飛び込んできたセナのささやきによって、僕は目を開けた。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:I'd been listening to a really pretentious conversation between two men I didn't recognize. I'd heard Sena's whispers in the gaps between their words, and it had woken me up.[%p]"

msgid "1100:相変わらず、僕とセナは密着している。[linebreak]瓦礫に囲まれ、脱出もままならない。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:We were still pressed together. The rubble was all around us and we couldn't escape.[%p]"

msgid "1200:[name]倉持[line]「君は君自身の意志で、この未来を選び取ってきた。すべては君の責任だ。だが１人で背負うには重すぎるだろう？\u3000神光の救いがもたらされれば、その重みも多少は減ろう」[%p]"
msgstr "1200:[name]倉持[line]You chose this future of your own free will. Everything that's happened is your responsibility. But it's far too great a burden for one person to bear, isn't it? The salvation of the Divine Light could lighten your burdens.[%p]"

msgid "1300:[name]波多野[line]「そうだ、私が選んだ。神光の導きに従った結果として、いや、あなたの言葉に従った結果としてだ」[%p]"
msgstr "1300:[name]波多野[line]Yes. This was my choice. I followed the guidance of the Divine Light. Or rather, I did what you told me to.[%p]"

msgid "1400:[name]セナ[line]「誰かいる。話し声が聞こえるだろ？」[%p]"
msgstr "1400:[name]セナ[line]Someone's out there. You can hear their voices, right?[%p]"

msgid "1500:僕はその問いかけにうなずく。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:I nodded.[%p]"

msgid "1600:２人の男の声が聞こえてくる。[linebreak]天成神光会がどうたら。[linebreak]少なくとも、救助隊じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:I could hear two men's voices. They were saying something about the Cosmic Church of the Divine Light. They weren't a rescue team, if nothing else.[%p]"

msgid "1700:[name]セナ[line]「あいつだ……あいつが、近くにいる……！」[%p]"
msgstr "1700:[name]セナ[line]It's him! He's close![%p]"

msgid "1800:セナが歯ぎしりをする音が、僕の耳にもはっきり届いた。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:This close, I could clearly hear the sound of her clenching her jaw.[%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]波多野[line]「言葉を飾るのはやめるんだ、倉持雄大。あなたの美辞麗句は、もう私の心には響かない」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]波多野[line]I've had enough of your fancy words, Yudai Kuramochi. Nothing you say matters to me anymore.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]倉持[line]「残念だ。もっとも、君がいなくてもすでにノアⅡは完成している。後は世界に向けて我らの意志を発信するのみだ」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]倉持[line]A shame. Of course, even without your help, Noah II is already complete. All that's left now is to send out our will to the rest of the world.[%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]波多野[line]「我らの、ではなく、あなたと、猪鼻康三の、だろう？」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]波多野[line]You don't mean “our” will. You mean your will, and the will of Kozo Inohana.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]猪鼻[line]「いかにも。サードメルトの実験成功によりプロジェクト・ノアは試験段階を終了した」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]猪鼻[line]Indeed. With the success of the Third Melt, Project Noah has passed the prototype stage.[%p]"

msgid "2300:３人目の男の声。[linebreak]いったい、なにを話してる？[linebreak]どこで、話してる？[%p]"
msgstr "2300:A third voice. What were they talking about? Where were they speaking?[%p]"

msgid "2400:少なくとも声が聞こえるっていうことは、僕らが埋もれている近くで会話をしているっていうことだ。僕らの上に積もっている瓦礫は、それほど多くないのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:If we could hear them, they had to be somewhere near the spot where we were buried. Maybe we weren't buried as deeply as I thought.[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]セナ[line]「はぁ……はぁ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]セナ[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "2600:セナが身じろぎする。[linebreak]その手が、僕の制服をきつく握りしめている。[linebreak]なにかに耐えるように、きつく。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:Sena was fidgeting. Her hands were clinging tightly to my uniform. Tightly, as if she was trying to keep control.[%p]"

msgid "2700:視線は伏せられていた。僕を見ようとしない。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:Her gaze was lowered. She wasn't looking at me.[%p]"

msgid "2800:[name]猪鼻[line]「これからの世界秩序は、３００人による統治から、２人による統治に変わるというわけだ。今日が、その夜明けだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "2800:[name]猪鼻[line]World order will no longer be kept by three hundred men, but by two. Today is the dawn of a new era.[%p]"

msgid "2900:と、いきなり視界に光が射し込んできた。[linebreak]ボロボロと、周囲の細かい瓦礫が崩れる。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:Suddenly, I saw light. The rubble around us began to collapse.[%p]"

msgid "3000:セナがハッと顔を上げる。[linebreak]頭の上、瓦礫の隙間から、手が伸びてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:Sena gasped and looked up. A hand was reaching down from above, in between the gaps in the rubble.[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]波多野[line]「無事か、セナ」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]波多野[line]Are you okay, Sena?[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]セナ[line]「お……まえ……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]セナ[line]Y-You...[%p]"

msgid "3300:セナがその手によって引っ張り出されていく。[linebreak]セナがどいたことで、隙間が広がり、重しもなくなって、僕はさっきよりずっと自由に動けるようになった。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:The hand pulled her out. With her off me, I could move much more easily than before.[%p]"

msgid "3400:開けられた隙間から這い出る。[linebreak]希ビルの一室。僕らが閉じ込められていた部屋だ。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:I crawled out of the gap. We were in a room in the Nozomi Building. It was the room we'd been trapped in.[%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]倉持[line]「君も野呂瀬同様に、我らが使ってやろうと言っているのに、それを拒否するとは。統治側ではなく、家畜として生きるのが望みかね？」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]倉持[line]I was willing to let you be useful, just like Norose, and yet you refuse. So, you'd rather live as cattle than be a ruler?[%p]"

msgid "3600:つり下げられていたいくつものモニタは、今はほとんどが落下して、画面が割れてしまっている。当然ながら画面にはなにも映っていない。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:Most of the monitors had fallen, and their screens had cracked. Of course, they were all black.[%p]"

msgid "3700:壁なども崩れかけていた。[linebreak]でも思ったほどの崩れ方じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:The walls were crumbling, too. But it wasn't as bad as I'd thought.[%p]"

msgid "3800:僕らは生き埋めになってはいたけど、瓦礫の量はそれほどじゃなく、[linebreak]やろうと思えば、自力で脱出することだってできたわけか。[linebreak]押し潰される恐怖で身動きが取れなかったのがバカみたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:We were buried alive, but not by that much rubble. We could've escaped any time we wanted to. I felt like an idiot for not moving because I was scared of being crushed.[%p]"

msgid "3900:[name]セナ[line]「…………っ」[%p]"
msgstr "3900:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "4000:[name]波多野[line]「セナ……」[%p]"
msgstr "4000:[name]波多野[line]Sena...[%p]"

msgid "4100:セナは、見知らぬ男と向かい合っていた。[linebreak]薄汚れたコートを身にまとった、濁った目をした男。[linebreak]その身なりはホームレスにしか見えない。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:Sena was standing in front of a man I didn't recognize. His eyes were milky, and he was wearing a filthy coat. He looked like he was homeless.[%p]"

msgid "4200:どこかで会ったような気がするけど、どこだったのかは思い出せなかった。もしかしたら、渋谷の街のどこかですれ違っただけなのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:I felt like I'd seen him somewhere before, but I couldn't remember where. Maybe we'd just passed each other in Shibuya somewhere.[%p]"

msgid "4300:その２人以外に、人影はない。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:There was no one there but the two of them.[%p]"

msgid "4400:僕らを罠にはめた、天成神光会の教祖と、衆議院議員、その２人の声は、きっと室内のどこかにあるスピーカーから聞こえてくるものだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:The two voices we'd heard, that of the Cosmic Church's leader and the Diet member, were coming out of a speaker somewhere in the room.[%p]"

msgid "4500:[name]倉持[line]「おや、波多野よ、どうやら親子で感動の対面を果たしたようだね」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]倉持[line]Oh, Hatano. I see you've had a touching reunion with your daughter.[%p]"

msgid "4600:親子……。[linebreak]セナと、この男が、親子？[linebreak]確かに“波多野”って名前は、前にセナから聞いたことがある。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:Daughter... Sena was his daughter? I remembered hearing the name “Hatano” from Sena before.[%p]"

msgid "4700:[name]猪鼻[line]「せいぜい、再会の喜びでも語っているがいい。そしてそこから眺めているのだな。世界が、変革していく様を」[%p]"
msgstr "4700:[name]猪鼻[line]I hope you enjoy it. And when you're done, you can watch as the world changes forever.[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]倉持[line]「ノアⅡをフル稼働させれば、渋谷だけでなく、世界中のすべての人間に作用を及ぼすことが可能だ。そのネットワークはすでに構築さ――」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]倉持[line]Once Noah II comes online at full power, its effects will extend to the entire world. The required network is already in place?[%p]"

msgid "4900:不意に、スピーカーからの声が途切れた。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:Suddenly, the voice from the speaker stopped.[%p]"

msgid "5000:奇妙な物音。[linebreak]スピーカーの電源が切れているわけじゃない。[linebreak]なにかが、変だ。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:I heard a strange sound. The power to the speakers hadn't shut off. Something had happened.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……！\u3000い、今のって……」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]拓巳[line]Ah! W-Was that...[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]波多野[line]「銃声……」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]波多野[line]A gunshot...[%p]"

msgid "5300:その銃声の後に、荒い息をつく男の、しゃがれた声が聞こえてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:After the gunshot, we heard panting, and a ragged, frail voice.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]猪鼻[line]「バ、バカな……。こんなはずでは……。私は、これから統治者に――」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]猪鼻[line]I-Impossible... This wasn't supposed to happen! I was supposed to rule the world...[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]猪鼻[line]「ぎゃああぁっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]猪鼻[line]Gyah![%p]"

msgid "5600:断末魔の叫びだった。[linebreak]それもすぐにブツンと切れて、それきりスピーカーは沈黙する。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:A dying scream. It ended midway, and no further sound came from the speaker.[%p]"

msgid "5700:異様な静けさ。[linebreak]なにが起きた……？[%p]"
msgstr "5700:There was a strange silence. What had just happened?[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]拓巳[line]「こ、殺されたんじゃ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]拓巳[line]W-Was he killed?[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]セナ[line]「殺された？\u3000誰に？」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]セナ[line]Killed? By who?[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]拓巳[line]「し、知らないよ……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't know.[%p]"

msgid "6100:あの２人は、どこから、スピーカーで語りかけていたんだろう。[linebreak]僕らがいるこの部屋の近くだろうか。[linebreak]少なくとも、このビルの一室なのは間違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:Where had they been when they were talking to us through that speaker? Somewhere close? It had to be somewhere in the building, at least.[%p]"

msgid "6200:ということは、あの２人を殺した犯人が、[linebreak]すぐ近くにいるっていうこと……。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:Which meant that whoever killed them, they were right nearby us.[%p]"

msgid "6300:[name]拓巳[line]「に、にげ、逃げようよ……。殺人鬼が、ここに来るかも……」[%p]"
msgstr "6300:[name]拓巳[line]L-Let's get out of here. The murderer might come here.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]セナ[line]「だから、殺人鬼って誰だ？\u3000なんであの２人は殺された？\u3000いや、殺されたと判断した根拠は！？」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]セナ[line]But who killed them? Why were they killed? No, what makes you think they were killed?![%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]波多野[line]「落ち着け、セナ」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]波多野[line]Calm down, Sena.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]セナ[line]「お前には聞いてないっ」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]セナ[line]I'm not talking to you.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]拓巳[line]「悲鳴、き、聞いたでしょ……っ。[linebreak]こ、殺されたとしか、思え、ないよ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]拓巳[line]Y-You heard the scream, right? T-They have to have been killed![%p]"

msgid "6800:殺したのは誰だ？『将軍』か？[linebreak]でも『将軍』も希の人間のはず……。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:But who killed them? Shogun? But Shogun was working for Nozomi, right?[%p]"

msgid "6900:いやいや、希の人間だっていうのは、単なる僕の推測だ。なんの根拠もない。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:No, that was just a guess I'd made. I didn't have any evidence for it at all.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]波多野[line]「逃げるのは、少し面倒だ」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]波多野[line]It might be a little difficult to get out of here.[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]波多野[line]「このビルは、崩れかかっている。あちこちに歪みが生じている」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]波多野[line]This building is falling apart. There are cracks everywhere.[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]波多野[line]「私がこの部屋に入ってきた直後に、入り口が瓦礫で塞がれてしまった」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]波多野[line]Just after I came into the room, the entrance was blocked by rubble.[%p]"

msgid "7300:波多野さんの言う通りだった。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:Hatano was right.[%p]"

msgid "7400:でも、壁などの崩れ方に比べて、瓦礫がやけに多いような気もする。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:But it felt like there was an awful lot of rubble on the ground compared to the damage on the walls.[%p]"

msgid "7500:違和感がある。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:It felt wrong.[%p]"

msgid "7600:とは言え、そもそも廃墟なんかに行った経験はないから、壁の崩れ方と瓦礫の量の関係なんて分かるわけがないんだけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:But of course, I'd never been to any abandoned buildings before. I really didn't know how much rubble was normal, or how walls looked when they collapsed.[%p]"

msgid "7700:はっきりしているのは、生き埋め状態からは脱出できたけど、結局のところ閉じ込められてることに変わりはないっていう状況。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:What I did know, however, was that we'd escaped from being buried alive, but we were still trapped.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]セナ[line]「ディソードで壊せばいい」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]セナ[line]I can just destroy it with my Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "7900:この部屋に閉じ込めれたときに聞こえていた、あの奇妙な共鳴音がやんでいることに、僕はようやく気付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:I finally realized that the strange, high-pitched noise I'd heard when we were locked in the room had vanished.[%p]"

msgid "8000:地震のせいでその音を出す装置――ポート、だっけ？――も壊れちゃったのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:The earthquake must've destroyed the device making the noise. The porter? Was that what they were called?[%p]"

msgid "8100:それなら、セナがなんとかしてくれるかも。[linebreak]僕はホッとして、セナが脱出路を作ってくれるのを待った。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:Maybe Sena could do something, then. Relieved, I waited for Sena to make us a way out.[%p]"

msgid "8200:でも彼女は、剣を出そうともせず、じっと波多野さんをにらみつけたままだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:But instead of summoning her sword, she was just staring at Hatano.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]セナ[line]「あの２人となにを話していた？」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]セナ[line]What were you talking about with those two?[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]波多野[line]「昔話だ。互いに分かり合うことのできない、ね」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]波多野[line]Old times. And how we'll never be able to come to an understanding.[%p]"

msgid "8500:[name]セナ[line]「分かり合うことのできない……？\u3000本当にそうか？\u3000今でも繋がりがあるんじゃないのか？」[%p]"
msgstr "8500:[name]セナ[line]Never? You're sure about that? You're sure you're not still connected to them, somehow?[%p]"

msgid "8600:[name]セナ[line]「この半年、どこでなにをしていた……！」[%p]"
msgstr "8600:[name]セナ[line]Where have you been these last six months? What have you been doing?[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]セナ[line]「今になってこの場所に都合よく現れたのはなぜだ！？\u3000このビルのどこかで、私たちをモニタしていたからじゃないのか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]セナ[line]Why did you appear here now, at such a convenient time? You were watching us somewhere in this building, weren't you?[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]波多野[line]「私はこの半年、渋谷を徘徊していただけの、死にたがりだ」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]波多野[line]I've spent the last six months wandering around Shibuya, waiting to die.[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]波多野[line]「天成神光会にも希テクノロジーにも、戻るつもりはない……」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]波多野[line]I wasn't planning on going back to the Church, or to Nozomi.[%p]"

msgid "9000:セナは小さく舌打ちして、今度は僕の方を見た。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:Sena snarled at him before turning to me.[%p]"

msgid "9100:[name]セナ[line]「あの２人が殺されたと思う根拠は？」[%p]"
msgstr "9100:[name]セナ[line]What makes you think those two were killed?[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]拓巳[line]「え、そ、それは、だから……」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]拓巳[line]Huh? B-Because I heard...[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]波多野[line]「彼らは、敵が多い」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]波多野[line]They have a lot of enemies.[%p]"

msgid "9400:波多野さんが割り込んでくる。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:Hatano interrupted.[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]波多野[line]「誰に殺されても納得できる」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]波多野[line]Any number of people could have killed them.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]セナ[line]「お前には聞いてないと言っているだろ」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]セナ[line]I told you. I'm not talking to you.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]拓巳[line]「で、でも、ほら、悲鳴とか、銃声が、聞こえて……」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]拓巳[line]B-But we heard the screams... and the gunshots.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]セナ[line]「本当に、そうか？」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]セナ[line]You're sure about that?[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]セナ[line]「単なる演技の可能性は？\u3000そもそもスピーカーから聞こえていたあの２人の声は、リアルタイムのものか？」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]セナ[line]It isn't possible that it's all an act? When we heard them speaking, how do we know it was in real time?[%p]"

msgid "10000:ど、どういうことだ……？[%p]"
msgstr "10000:W-What did she mean?[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]セナ[line]「地震対策がしっかりしてる日本で、希グループという日本を代表する巨大企業の本社ビルが、これほどの地震被害を受けている……」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]セナ[line]Japanese building codes take earthquakes seriously, and we're inside the HQ of one the nation's biggest companies. They wouldn't have skimped on the construction costs. And look at the size of the damage around us.[%p]"

msgid "10200:[name]セナ[line]「それだけ、とんでもない地震が起きたということだ」[%p]"
msgstr "10200:[name]セナ[line]The earthquake that just hit was massive.[%p]"

msgid "10300:[name]セナ[line]「そんな状況で、なぜあの２人は、この部屋のスピーカーで、ベラベラと、裏事情を話してくれたんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "10300:[name]セナ[line]So if we just had a massive earthquake, why were those two sitting in front of microphones and telling us all their secrets?[%p]"

msgid "10400:セナは確認するかのように、一語一語をはっきり区切って、そう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:There was a small gap between her words, as if she was still trying to figure this out for herself.[%p]"

msgid "10500:裏事情……か。ノアⅡがどうとか、サードメルトがどうとか。僕にはほとんど理解できなかったけど。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:Their secrets... Noah II, the Third Melt... I hadn't understood most of what they'd said.[%p]"

msgid "10600:[name]セナ[line]「これ見よがしに感じる。ヤツらは裏事情を、私たちに意図的に聞かせる必要があったのかもしれない」[%p]"
msgstr "10600:[name]セナ[line]It feels planned. Like there was some reason they needed us to hear it.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]セナ[line]「あの２人は、実在しているのか？\u3000地震が起きる前に、すでに死んでいた可能性は？」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]セナ[line]Are those two even real? Is it possible they died before the earthquake?[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]セナ[line]「西條、私もお前も、このビルに乗り込んでから[linebreak]あの２人とは一度も会っていない。そうだな？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]セナ[line]Nishijo, we didn't run into them once after coming inside this building, did we? Am I wrong?[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]拓巳[line]「で、でも、モニタで喋ってた……」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]拓巳[line]B-But they were talking on the monitor.[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]セナ[line]「モニタの中で、だろう。実際に会ったわけじゃない。あんなもの、いくらでも細工できる」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]セナ[line]On the monitor, right? We didn't actually see them. There are any number of ways to fake that.[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]セナ[line]「スピーカーについても、言うまでもない」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]セナ[line]And even more ways to fake the voices from the speakers.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]セナ[line]「なにか変だ。不可解だ。それに私は――」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]セナ[line]Something's not right. This doesn't make sense. And I'm...[%p]"

msgid "11300:セナの言葉を遮って、波多野さんが見開いた目を僕に向けていた。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Hatano interrupted her. He was looking at me intently.[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]波多野[line]「西條、拓巳くん。君が、そうなのか」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]波多野[line]Takumi Nishijo. So that's you.[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]波多野[line]「そうか。君が」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]波多野[line]I see. You're the one, then.[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]セナ[line]「動くな」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]セナ[line]Don't move.[%p]"

msgid "11700:無視されたセナが、その波多野さんに鋭い声で呼びかける。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:Sena's tone was sharp as a knife.[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]セナ[line]「もう一度聞く。お前は、なぜここにいる？」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]セナ[line]I'll ask again. What are you doing here?[%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]波多野[line]「……お前たちを助けに来た。いや……殺されに来た、というのが本心かもしれない」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]波多野[line]I came to save you. No... I came to be killed, to tell the truth.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]セナ[line]「心配しなくても、すぐに殺してやる。でもその前に、質問に答えろ」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]セナ[line]Don't worry. I'll kill you soon. But first, answer my question.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]セナ[line]「私たちがここにいることを、どうして知っていた？」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]セナ[line]How did you know we were here?[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]波多野[line]「強い、心の呼びかけを感じた」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]波多野[line]I felt a strong cry from the heart.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]セナ[line]「ギガロマニアックスでもないお前が、どうしてそれを感じることができるんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]セナ[line]You're no Gigalomaniac. How were you able to feel anything?[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]セナ[line]「いや、ギガロマニアックスでさえ“心の呼びかけ”なんていう曖昧な妄想を感知できるのは、ごく一部だけだ」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]セナ[line]No, only a small fraction of Gigalomaniacs are capable of hearing anything like a “cry from the heart.”[%p]"

msgid "12500:例えば、こずぴぃとか。[linebreak]そう言えば、こずぴぃはどうしてるんだろう。地震に巻き込まれたんだろうか。無事ならいいけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:Like Kozupii, maybe. Come to think of it, where was Kozupii? Was she caught in the earthquake? I hoped she was okay.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]セナ[line]「本当に、感じたのか？\u3000最初から、知っていたんじゃないのか？\u3000私たちが、この部屋におびき寄せられたことを」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]セナ[line]Did you really feel it? Or did you know about this from the start? Know that we were lured here.[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]波多野[line]「冷静になれ、セナ。憎しみに心を支配されているぞ」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]波多野[line]Calm down, Sena. Your hatred is taking over your mind.[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]セナ[line]「冷静になれだと？\u3000ずっと殺したいと思っていた人間を目の前にして、冷静でいられるはずがないだろ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]セナ[line]Calm down? The person I've wanted to kill for ages is right here in front of me! How am I supposed to stay calm?[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]波多野[line]「考え過ぎてはいけない。物事は陰謀論ほど複雑ではなく、もっとシンプルだ――」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]波多野[line]Don't overthink things. This isn't a complicated conspiracy. It's quite simple—[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]セナ[line]「この場に、お前が現れるのは、都合が良すぎるんだっ」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]セナ[line]There's no good goddamn reason for you to be here right now![%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]セナ[line]「最初から仕組まれたことじゃないのか？」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]セナ[line]This whole thing was a setup, wasn't it?[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]セナ[line]「この部屋におびき出されて監禁された私たち。地震。直後に現れたお前という存在。スピーカーからの、これ見よがしの陰謀論風な演説と、その不可解な中断」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]セナ[line]We were lured here. Trapped. Then the earthquake happened. And then you show up, right in time to save us. And at the same time, there's this long speech right out of a conspiracy thriller coming out of the speakers, which cuts off with an ominous gunshot.[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]セナ[line]「そもそも、この部屋が希のビルである確証もない。私たちが気絶している間に、別の場所に運び込まれていたとしたら？」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]セナ[line]There's no evidence this is even the Nozomi building. What if we were moved somewhere else while we were passed out?[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]セナ[line]「希のビルに内装だけ模してある部屋。地震など起きていなくて、散乱している瓦礫も人為的に配置したもの」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]セナ[line]This room looks like the one in the Nozomi building. But it's not. There was no earthquake. The rubble here was placed by someone.[%p]"

msgid "13500:セナが言葉を紡げば紡ぐほど、僕はなにを信じればいいのか分からなくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:The more she talked, the less I knew what to believe.[%p]"

msgid "13600:自分の存在に対する拠り所が、ひとつずつ、ガラガラと崩れていくような感覚。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:It felt like all the things I'd thought I knew were crumbling, one by one.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]波多野[line]「疑心暗鬼は己を滅ぼす。気をしっかり持て、セナ」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]波多野[line]Paranoia will get you killed. Get yourself together, Sena.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]セナ[line]「お前に名前を呼ばれたくはない。会話をするつもりもない。質問に答えろ！」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]セナ[line]I don't want to hear you say my name. I'm not here to have a conversation with you. Now answer me![%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]波多野[line]「地震は起きた。確実にだ。渋谷のあらゆる建物は、崩壊しかかっている。死傷者は４桁以上だろう」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]波多野[line]The earthquake was real. It happened. Almost every building in Shibuya has either collapsed, or is about to. Casualties will likely run into the four digits.[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]セナ[line]「それを証明する方法を持っているのか？」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]セナ[line]Do you have a way to prove that?[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]波多野[line]「その壁を崩してみるといい。お前の、ディソードで」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]波多野[line]Destroy that wall with your Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "14200:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14200:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14300:セナは右手を振り払うような仕草をした。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Sena waved her right hand as if knocking something away.[%p]"

msgid "14400:一瞬にして、そこにディソードが姿を現す。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:The Di-Sword appeared instantly.[%p]"

msgid "14500:セナは剣を構えると、躊躇なく壁に向かって振り下ろした。[linebreak]ディソードは滑らかに壁をスライスした。まるで熱したナイフでバターを切ったかのよう。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:She brought it down on the wall without any hesitation whatsoever. It sliced clean through, like a hot knife through butter.[%p]"

msgid "14600:壁が崩れる。[linebreak]最初に、強い、冷たい風が吹き込んできた。[linebreak]崩れた壁の向こうにある光景が、僕らの前に露わになる。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:The wall collapsed. And a cold, strong wind blew into our faces. We could see what lay beyond it.[%p]"

msgid "14700:そこに見えたのは――[%p]"
msgstr "14700:What I saw was...[%p]"

msgid "14800:文字通り、死の廃墟と化した渋谷。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:A city of death.[%p]"

msgid "14900:ほんの数時間前まで、あれだけの人を呑み込み、きらびやかな装飾で溢れ、街灯ビジョンから大音量でおしゃれな映像を垂れ流していた、若者の街。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Just a few hours ago, Shibuya had been a bustling city, filled with bright lights and noise blasting from the big TVs in the square.[%p]"

msgid "15000:それが今や、象徴的な建物のほとんどは崩壊し、それを免れたものも傾き、あるいはいくつもの致命的な亀裂に侵食され。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:Now, almost every building I recognized as a landmark had collapsed. The ones that hadn't were either tilting over, or had huge cracks running down them.[%p]"

msgid "15100:道を走る車は一台もなく。アスファルトはある場所で陥没し、別の場所では隆起し、黒々とした煙があちこちから立ち上って、濁った空へと消えていっている。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Not a single car was running through the streets. In some places, the asphalt had fallen in. In others it had risen up. There was black smoke rising up all over the city, vanishing into a muddy gray sky.[%p]"

msgid "15200:それが、ビルの高層階から見下ろした、今の渋谷だった。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:That was what we saw as we looked down from the skyscraper.[%p]"

msgid "15300:セナは疑心暗鬼になっているだけだ。それに僕も引きずられている。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:Sena was just being paranoid, and it had been having an influence on me.[%p]"

msgid "15400:間違いなく、ここは希本社ビルの３１階で、地震も起きたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:This was, without doubt, the thirty-first floor of Nozomi HQ, and the earthquake was real.[%p]"

msgid "15500:このビルも、いつ崩れるか分からない。[linebreak]もし崩れたら、僕なんてひとたまりもない。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:There was no telling when the building would collapse. And if it did, I'd be dead in seconds.[%p]"

msgid "15600:大量の瓦礫に押し潰されて終わりだ。死体すら発見されることなく、永久に埋もれたままにされてしまうかも。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I'd be crushed under a hundred tons of rubble. Maybe they'd never even find my corpse.[%p]"

msgid "15700:早く脱出した方がいい。[linebreak]僕は身を震わせつつ、部屋の中を見回した。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:I should get out of here, now. I shuddered and looked around the room.[%p]"

msgid "15800:……ん？[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Hmm?[%p]"

msgid "15900:本能的に、それを目に留めていた。[linebreak]床に転がっている、モニタ。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:My eyes stopped, instinctively, on one of the objects on the floor. One of the monitors.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]セナ[line]「単なる地震で、ここまで被害が大きくなるはずがない」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]セナ[line]An earthquake wouldn't cause this kind of damage.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]セナ[line]「ノアⅡか？」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]セナ[line]Was it Noah II?[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]波多野[line]「そうだ。サードメルト。ノアⅡの最終稼働実験だ」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]波多野[line]That's right. The Third Melt. The final test of Noah II's capabilities.[%p]"

msgid "16300:液晶画面は半分ほどが割れてしまっていて、なにも表示されない。[linebreak]残り半分の画面は、粘り強く点灯していた。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:Half of its LCD screen had shattered completely. The other half was still turned on.[%p]"

msgid "16400:さっき見たときは、点いてなかったような気がするけど、あまり自信はない。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:It felt like it hadn't been turned on a moment ago, but I couldn't be sure.[%p]"

msgid "16500:[name]セナ[line]「サードメルト……。お前もかかわっているのか？」[%p]"
msgstr "16500:[name]セナ[line]The Third Melt... Are you part of it?[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]波多野[line]「言っただろう。私は、もう半年以上前に、希から逃げ出した人間だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]波多野[line]I told you, I ran away from Nozomi over six months ago.[%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]セナ[line]「希だけじゃない。[linebreak]お前は、私や、母さんや、妹からも逃げたんだ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]セナ[line]Not just Nozomi. You ran from me, Mom, and my little sister, too![%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]波多野[line]「……ああ。認める」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]波多野[line]Yeah. I admit it.[%p]"

msgid "16900:セナと波多野さんのギスギスしたやり取りを半分聞き流し、僕はモニタの前にしゃがみ込んだ。[linebreak]文字だ。テキストが表示されている。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I half-ignored Sena and Hatano's awkward conversation as I knelt down in front of the monitor. Letters. There were letters on the screen.[%p]"

